205
00:16:09,469 --> 00:16:12,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, kau bukan On Dal.</font>

206
00:16:16,542 --> 00:16:17,743
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi Moo-myung...</font>

207
00:16:20,947 --> 00:16:21,981
<font color=#FFFF00>...tolong menghilanglah.</font>

208
00:16:24,283 --> 00:16:28,454
<font color=#FFFF00>Demi Pyeong-gang,
