209
00:17:25,144 --> 00:17:26,379
<font color=#FFFF00>Segitu sukanya kau padaku?</font>

210
00:17:28,180 --> 00:17:29,415
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau belum tidur?</font>

211
00:17:31,150 --> 00:17:35,054
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak bisa tidur karena
