231
00:18:54,266 --> 00:18:55,768
<font color=#FFFF00>"Menahannya."</font>

232
00:18:57,637 --> 00:19:00,106
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku suka ekspresi itu.</font>

233
00:19:01,607 --> 00:19:02,608
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku belum pernah mendengarnya.</font>

234
00:19:02,675 --> 00:19:06,846
<font color=#FFFF00>Pria seperti apa yang pernah
