235
00:19:08,347 --> 00:19:09,348
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku...</font>

236
00:19:10,583 --> 00:19:12,084
<font color=#FFFF00>Kaulah orang pertama yang kupacari.</font>

237
00:19:12,551 --> 00:19:14,553
<font color=#FFFF00>Lihatlah aktingmu itu.</font>

238
00:19:15,221 --> 00:19:18,491
<font color=#FFFF00>Pasti ada beberapa pria...</font>

239
00:19:18,557 --> 00:19:20,493
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang pernah kau miliki.</font>

240
00:19:20,559 --> 00:19:23,496
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau cuman berpikir aku pernah
