276
00:21:26,185 --> 00:21:27,953
<font color=#FFFF00>"Mereka yang tidak
berasal dari dunia ini..."</font>

277
00:21:32,792 --> 00:21:35,394
<font color=#FFFF00>On Dal, aku...</font>

278
00:21:38,063 --> 00:21:39,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak perlu mengatakannya.</font>

279
00:21:40,499 --> 00:21:42,902
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan katakan itu.</font>

280
00:21:44,870 --> 00:21:47,706
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak peduli. Aku hanya ingin...</font>

281
00:21:52,378 --> 00:21:53,979
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau berada di sisiku.</font>

282
00:21:54,914 --> 00:21:57,183
<font color=#FFFF00>- On Dal.
